TASK_TITLE=Fix send-keys delivery — paste-buffer fails on Claude CLI, direct send-keys with shorter messages
TASK_STATUS=done
TASK_TYPE=bugfix
TASK_DESCRIPTION=Paste-buffer approach in doey_send_verified does not work reliably with Claude CLI instances. The pasted text is not visible in the prompt at all — tmux history shows only the idle prompt. Root cause from task 249 research: (1) Escape between paste and Enter clears input, (2) Go SendVerified has no readiness gate, (3) timing too fast. Fix: remove Escape before Enter in paste-buffer path (doey-send.sh:164, sendverified.go:72), add waitForPrompt() to Go SendVerified (sendverified.go:18), increase Go short-msg delay or use direct send-keys for all messages. Research report: /tmp/doey/doey/research/task_249_sendkeys_audit.md
